data.description: Wyndham Falls Estates is just outside The Perimeter, located only 3 miles to I-285, offering quick access to everything the City of Atlanta has to offer including shopping, dining, recreation and entertainment. Your style, your way. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected.® Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. There is room to grow in this spacious design offering an extended foyer that includes extra storage. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected.® Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. The central family room opens to the kitchen and a casual dining area, perfect for entertaining. Cabinet color options include gray, white and espresso. Plus, enjoy the outdoors with a covered patio that overlooks the back yard. Upstairs offers a convenient laundry, generous bedrooms including a private bedroom suite with spacious bath and oversized closet. Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
